---
title: Lemon Yoghurt-Roasted Chicken with Flatbreads, Braised Eggplant & Crumbly Cheese
description: One bite of this tender roast chicken, accompanied with elegant sides: braised eggplant with crumbly cheese, a crisp radish salad
and flatbreads makes it clear why the simple things are hard to beat.
